dcterms:description: The rolling bearing HRB6308 is selected as the experimental bearing. The dataset includes vibration signals collected under various fault conditions, including normal, inner ring fault, outer ring fault, and compound faults. A total of 14,000 samples were collected, with each fault type having 2,000 samples.
dcterms:title: ABLT-1A Bearing Dataset 6308

dcterms:creator: W. Mao

dcterms:description: The rolling bearing HRB6205 is selected as the experimental bearing. The dataset includes vibration signals collected under various fault conditions at different rotational speeds. A total of 24,000 samples were collected, with each fault type having 1,000 samples at four different speeds.
dcterms:title: ABLT-1A Bearing Dataset 6205
